<item>
            <title>[FLINK-1385] Add option to YARN client to disable resource availability checks</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1385</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The YARN client checks which resources are available in the cluster at the time of the initial deployment.&lt;br/&gt;
If somebody wants to deploy a Flink YARN session to a full YARN cluster, the Flink Client will reject the session.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m going to add an option which disables the check. The YARN session will then allocate new containers as they become available in the cluster.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
